<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.5">
<l>muṉṉalōrveḷ ḷipperuma laikkuṭṭaṉ moṭumoṭu viraintōṭap</l>
<l>piṉṉaittoṭarnta tōrkaruma laikkuṭṭaṟ peyarntaṭi yiṭuvatupōl</l>
<l>paṉṉiyula kamparavi yōvāppu kaḻppala tēvaṉeṉṉum</l>
<l>taṉṉampiyō ṭappiṟkūṭaccelvāṉ taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like when the child [like] a big, good, white mountain, rumbling, runs swiftly ahead</l>
<l>[and] the child [like] a black mountain that follows after moves forward,</l>
<l>the world consideratly praises Baladeva of unending fame</l>
<l>while his little brother runs after [him];</l>
<l>will the one who went to join [him] not come with a tottering walk?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
